gameRecap.title: Game Recap: 76ers 126, Trail Blazers 98
gameRecap.excerpt: Led by Joel Embiids 35 points, 15 rebounds, seven assists, and six blocks, the 76ers defeated the Trail Blazers, 126-98. Tyrese Maxey added 26 points, 10 rebounds, and four assists for the 76ers, while Shaedon Sharpe tallied a team-high 20 points for the Trail Blazers in the losing effort. The 76ers improve to 2-1 on the season, while the Trail Blazers fall to 0-3.
